channel.title: I Can't log out of my server once I log in. Help!

Ok hi. Well, I was editting my server's client.java and when I compiled, I ran the server and played it. I found out that I wasn't able to logout any more. Can anyone please help me fix it? Help would be really appreciated.
Thanks.
